(8, 2, 'DCA', 'DIPLOMA IN COMPUTER APPLICATION', '1666067002897.jpg', '', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">DCA is a</span><strong style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"> Diploma in Computer Application</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">. It is a one-year computer-based diploma or course. The course is intended to provide learners with basic, realistic and technological details pertaining to programming tools and applications which are used in our everyday lives. An intermediate or 12th class in any stream from a recognized board or university is the required qualification needed for this program.</span></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" arial,=\"\" \"noto=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif,=\"\" \"apple=\"\" color=\"\" emoji\",=\"\" \"segoe=\"\" ui=\"\" symbol\",=\"\" emoji\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(28,=\"\" 28,=\"\" 28);\"=\"\"><b><u>Course Contents -</u></b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, \" sans-serif\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(51,=\"\" 51,=\"\" 51);=\"\" background-image:=\"\" initial;=\"\" background-position:=\"\" background-size:=\"\" background-repeat:=\"\" background-attachment:=\"\" background-origin:=\"\" background-clip:=\"\" initial;\"=\"\">1.  Computer Fundamentals.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, \" sans-serif\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(51,=\"\" 51,=\"\" 51);=\"\" background-image:=\"\" initial;=\"\" background-position:=\"\" background-size:=\"\" background-repeat:=\"\" background-attachment:=\"\" background-origin:=\"\" background-clip:=\"\" initial;\"=\"\">2.  Computer Overview( Software and Hardware).<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, \" sans-serif\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(51,=\"\" 51,=\"\" 51);=\"\" background-image:=\"\" initial;=\"\" background-position:=\"\" background-size:=\"\" background-repeat:=\"\" background-attachment:=\"\" background-origin:=\"\" background-clip:=\"\" initial;\"=\"\">3.  Ms-Paint<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, \" sans-serif\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(51,=\"\" 51,=\"\" 51);=\"\" background-image:=\"\" initial;=\"\" background-position:=\"\" background-size:=\"\" background-repeat:=\"\" background-attachment:=\"\" background-origin:=\"\" background-clip:=\"\" initial;\"=\"\">4.  WordPad<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, \" sans-serif\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(51,=\"\" 51,=\"\" 51);=\"\" background-image:=\"\" initial;=\"\" background-position:=\"\" background-size:=\"\" background-repeat:=\"\" background-attachment:=\"\" background-origin:=\"\" background-clip:=\"\" initial;\"=\"\">5.  Notepad<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, \" sans-serif\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(51,=\"\" 51,=\"\" 51);=\"\" background-image:=\"\" initial;=\"\" background-position:=\"\" background-size:=\"\" background-repeat:=\"\" background-attachment:=\"\" background-origin:=\"\" background-clip:=\"\" initial;\"=\"\">6.  Windows XP and 2007 ,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, \" sans-serif\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(51,=\"\" 51,=\"\" 51);=\"\" background-image:=\"\" initial;=\"\" background-position:=\"\" background-size:=\"\" background-repeat:=\"\" background-attachment:=\"\" background-origin:=\"\" background-clip:=\"\" initial;\"=\"\">7.  MS-Office XP/2007<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, \" sans-serif\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(51,=\"\" 51,=\"\" 51);=\"\" background-image:=\"\" initial;=\"\" background-position:=\"\" background-size:=\"\" background-repeat:=\"\" background-attachment:=\"\" background-origin:=\"\" background-clip:=\"\" initial;\"=\"\">            Ms-Word<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, \" sans-serif\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(51,=\"\" 51,=\"\" 51);=\"\" background-image:=\"\" initial;=\"\" background-position:=\"\" background-size:=\"\" background-repeat:=\"\" background-attachment:=\"\" background-origin:=\"\" background-clip:=\"\" initial;\"=\"\">            Ms-Excel<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, \" sans-serif\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(51,=\"\" 51,=\"\" 51);=\"\" background-image:=\"\" initial;=\"\" background-position:=\"\" background-size:=\"\" background-repeat:=\"\" background-attachment:=\"\" background-origin:=\"\" background-clip:=\"\" initial;\"=\"\">            Ms-PowerPoint<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, \" sans-serif\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(51,=\"\" 51,=\"\" 51);=\"\" background-image:=\"\" initial;=\"\" background-position:=\"\" background-size:=\"\" background-repeat:=\"\" background-attachment:=\"\" background-origin:=\"\" background-clip:=\"\" initial;\"=\"\">            Ms-Access.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, \" sans-serif\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(51,=\"\" 51,=\"\" 51);=\"\" background-image:=\"\" initial;=\"\" background-position:=\"\" background-size:=\"\" background-repeat:=\"\" background-attachment:=\"\" background-origin:=\"\" background-clip:=\"\" initial;\"=\"\"> 8.  Multimedia\r\nand E commerce concepts.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 18pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, \" sans-serif\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(51,=\"\" 51,=\"\" 51);=\"\" background-image:=\"\" initial;=\"\" background-position:=\"\" background-size:=\"\" background-repeat:=\"\" background-attachment:=\"\" background-origin:=\"\" background-clip:=\"\" initial;\"=\"\">9.  Internet Browsing and email handling</span></p><h3 style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.1; color: rgb(129, 53, 136); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 19px;\"><b><u>Job profile after DCA course</u></b></h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">A few popular job profiles for candidates after completing the DCA course are listed below.</p><ul style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><li style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">Accountant</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">Computer operator</li></ul><p style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\"><b>Why Diploma in Computer Application From Us?</b></p><ul><li style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">Important for Government Job point of view</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">Market Demand</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">Gain Experience</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">Polish Your Knowledge</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">100% Practical</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">Expert Faculty</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">Best Study Environment</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">Placement Assistance</li></ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 18pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" \"sans-serif\";\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', 6, 3000, '17-10-2022', 1),
(10, 1, 'ADCA', 'ADVANCE DIPLOMA IN COMPUTE APPLCATION', '1677691424886.png', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, \"sans-serif\"; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">1.  Computer Fundamentals.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, \"sans-serif\"; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">2.  Computer Overview( Software and Hardware).<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, \"sans-serif\"; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">3.  Ms-Paint<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, \"sans-serif\"; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">4.  WordPad<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, \"sans-serif\"; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">5.  Notepad<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, \"sans-serif\"; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">6.  Windows XP and 2007 ,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, \"sans-serif\"; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">7.  MS-Office XP/2007<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, \"sans-serif\"; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">            Ms-Word<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, \"sans-serif\"; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">            Ms-Excel<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, \"sans-serif\"; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">            Ms-PowerPoint<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, \"sans-serif\"; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); backgr