(1, 'KYP', 'Important: Admission Dates for May 2023 Batch!!', '', '', '<p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border: 0px; font-family: Oswald, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28.9px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241);\">Dear SDCs,</p><p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border: 0px; font-family: Oswald, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28.9px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241);\">Admission Process will be enable on Solar Portal for&nbsp;<strong style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">May&nbsp;2023&nbsp;</strong>Batch of&nbsp;<strong style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">KYP SDCs, KYP P</strong><img src=\"data:image/webp;base64,', '30-04-2023', 1);
